Package org.anchoranalysis.mpp.feature.energy.marks

Class VoxelizedMarksWithEnergy

Object
VoxelizedMarksWithEnergy
public final class VoxelizedMarksWithEnergy
extends Object
A collection of marks, their voxelized equivalents, and associated energy.

i.e. A MarksWithEnergyBreakdown together with the cached voxelization calculations.

Author:
Owen Feehan
